Booking Forms

Make the booking process as easy as possible for your customers with a complete and clean online booking form that allows you to collect all the data needed to make a reservation.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_column_text]

Instant Booking

Guests simply choose their travel dates to book with you immediately. It doesn’t require any kind of approval from the host prior to booking if the chosen dates are available.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][vc_column_text]

Booking Calendar

Keep your reservations organized in a friendly booking calendar interface. The calendar is fully responsive and looks great on any desktop or mobile device.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1540484271922{margin-bottom: 30px !important;padding-right: 30px !important;padding-left: 30px !important;background-color: #ffffff !important;}"][vc_column][homey-section-title homey_section_title="About Homey" homey_section_subtitle="" homey_section_title_align="text-left" homey_section_title_color="" fontsize_title="" lineheight_title="" fontsize_subtitle="" lineheight_subtitle=""][vc_column_text]

Homey is a premium WordPress theme for booking, accommodation, and rentals. Whether you are a rental business owner looking to build a website for your company or a web designer seeking a perfect WordPress theme for your next project, you are certain to appreciate the numerous features and benefits that our options panel offers to customize your site and adapt it to your business model.

The user experience is important if you want to be an industry leader. The clean design style with flat elements perfectly integrates into an easy-to-use user interface without compromise in your ability to customize the design.

This is not a theme that only takes care of the front of a rental online business. This is also a WordPress-based booking platform which allows you to receive reservations, accept payments, manage your properties and get in touch with your customers. The functions of booking, payment, advanced search and booking management make Homey the most suitable solution for those users who want to offer their properties for rent.
